nodes.text: The crime lord Kleb Zellock operated a criminal organization in 15 BBY. He operated out of Doodnik's Café in the frontier mining town of Tyne's Horky on a planet of the same name. His organization dealt in bounty hunting, smuggling, claim-jumping and gun-running. In 15 BBY, local miner Jann Tosh and his trusty droid sidekicks C-3PO and R2-D2 brought Zellock to justice.
